msgstr "<varname>MKVPROPEDIT_DEBUG</varname>, <varname>MKVTOOLNIX_DEBUG</varname> とその短縮形 <varname>MTX_DEBUG</varname>"

#. type: Content of: <refentry><refsect1><variablelist><varlistentry><listitem><para>
#: doc/man/mkvpropedit.xml:879
